title: Watch: gugudan Is Bold And Fabulous In New Music Video For "A Girl Like Me" | Soompi
text:
Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
gugudan is back with a new track! 
The girl group released their latest comeback music video on February 27 at 6 p.m. KST, and the music video showcases their bold and fashionable new image as well as a variety of fun and colorful sets. 
gugudan’s comeback album “Act 2. Narcissus” consists of six tracks including their title track “A Girl Like Me.” One of their follow up tracks is also written by VIXX’s Ravi. 
Check out the music video for “A Girl Like Me” below!
